   <topic>API_GETUSERNAME Function</topic>
     <description>API_GETUSERNAME() returns the name of Windows logon name of the current user</description>

   <syntax>Name_String as C = API_GetUserName()</syntax>
   
   <example><![CDATA[? API_GETUSERNAME()
= "ALincoln"]]></example>
   <limitations>Desktop applications only.</limitations>
